Serial output:

I initially faced problems with getting a proper graph i.e. my graph looked more like a representation of bits 0 or 1 instead of a smooth curve. I realised the problem was with the potentiometer rather than the code which was mapping the values.
After correcting that I was able to receive the values properly.

